{{main|气旋西纳}}
11月20日，[[瓦利斯岛|瓦利斯岛]]以西的南太平洋辐合区发展出弱热带低气压，[[斐济气象局|斐济气象局]]驻[[楠迪|楠迪]]热带气旋警报中心开始对之进行监控<ref name="Sina TCR">{{cite report | title = Tropical Cyclone Sina, November 24 - 30, 1990 | author2 = Nadi Tropical Cyclone Warning Center | publisher = Fiji Meteorological Service | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.pacificdisaster.net/pdnadmin/data/original/JB_DM393b_FJI_1990_TC_Sina.pdf | type = Tropical Cyclone Report 90/6 | author = Prasad, Rajendra | date = 1992-07-03 | accessdate = 2015-04-24 | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053736/http://www.pacificdisaster.net/pdnadmin/data/original/JB_DM393b_FJI_1990_TC_Sina.pdf }}</ref><ref name="TCF pred">{{cite journal | author = Ward, Graham F.A | date = 1995-03-01 | title = Prediction of tropical cyclone formation in terms of sea-surface temperatures vorticity and vertical windshear | issue = 1 | volume = 44 | pages = 63–64 | publisher = Australian Bureau of Meteorology | journal = Australian meteorological magazine (Australian Meteorological and Oceanographic Journal) | url = http://www.bom.gov.au/amoj/docs/1995/ward.pdf | accessdate = 2015-04-24 | format = PDF | archive-date = 2013-10-20 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6KVyhXfyN?url=http://www.bom.gov.au/amoj/docs/1995/ward.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。接下来3天里，系统向西北偏西方向的[[罗图马|罗图马]]移动，联合台风警报中心于11月24日将之归类为热带低气压，编号第三{{lang|en|P}}号热带气旋<ref name="Sina TCR" /><ref name="JTWC Verification" />。斐济气象局驻楠迪热带气旋警报中心宣布，系统在罗图马西北方向约425公里洋面达到[[热带气旋风级|澳大利亚热带气旋强度分级]]下的一级热带气旋强度，并将之命名为“西纳”（{{lang|en|Sina}}）<ref name="Sina TCR" /><ref name="Wellington BT" />。次日气旋总体向[[罗盘方位|西南偏西]]方向前进，并继续强化至发展出[[风眼|风眼]]，但前进方向很不稳定，形成小规模环形路径<ref name="Sina TCR" />。这天的卫星图像显示，西纳的风眼变得非常清晰，气旋增强的同时，也因受上层转向气流影响而朝东南方向和斐济移动，并且走向很不稳定<ref name="Sina TCR" />。当晚，斐济气象局驻楠迪热带气旋警报中心宣布风暴达到[[最大持续风速|10分钟持续风速]]每小时140公里的最高强度，属三级强烈热带气旋标准<ref name="Wellington BT" /><ref name="Sina MWL">{{cite journal | title = Hurricane Alley: Cyclones of the Southeast Pacific Ocean 1990–1991: Tropical Cyclone Sina November 24 – 30, 1990 | author = Fiji Meteorological Service | journal = Mariners Weather Log | year = 1992 | volume = 36 | issue = 4: Fall 1992 | page = 54 | oclc = 648466886 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Oceanographic Data Center | editor = DeAngellis, Richard M | id = {{hdl|2027/uiug.30112104094179}} | issn = 0025-3367}}</ref>。

次日清晨，联合台风警报中心宣布西纳达到1分钟持续风力时速140公里的最高强度，相当于[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的四级飓风<ref name="Sina BT">{{cite report | title = Tropical Cyclone 03P (Sina) best track analysis | author2 = Naval Western Oceanography Center | publisher = United States Navy, United States Air Force | author = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | accessdate = 2015-04-24 | archivedate = 2013-10-04 | deadurl = no | format = TXT | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131004153958/http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/best_tracks/1991/1991s-bsh/bsh031991.txt | url = http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/best_tracks/1991/1991s-bsh/bsh031991.txt | date =  }}</ref>。气旋在这天接下来的大部分时间里都保持在最高强度，然后在从维提岛以南约40公里洋面经过时开始逐渐减弱，于11月28从[[瓦图莱莱岛|瓦图莱莱岛]]、[[莫阿拉群岛|莫阿拉群岛]]和南部[[拉乌群岛|拉乌群岛]]上空经过<ref name="Sina TCR" />。11月29日清晨，风暴减弱成澳大利亚热带气旋强度分级下的二级热带气旋，然后从汤加的[[汤加塔布岛|汤加塔布岛]]北部经过<ref name="Sina TCR" /><ref name="Wellington BT" />。系统这天向东面的南库克群岛逼近，并在此期间进一步减弱<ref name="Sina BT" />。次日清晨，气旋从纽埃以南约160公里海域经过，然后再于当晚大幅回转向东南偏南逼近南库克群岛。受强烈的垂直风切变和[[海面温度|海面温度]]降低的共同影响，西纳迅速减弱并转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。<ref name="Sina TCR" />此后几天里，西纳的温带残留保持向东南方向前进，于12月4日被[[纬度|南纬]]50°附近的[[低压槽|低压槽]]吸收<ref name="SPAC90-91SS" />。

西纳没有造成人员丧生，但在斐济、汤加、纽埃和南库克群岛导致了价值超过1850万美元的破坏<ref name="SPAC90-91SS" />。风暴来袭前，数百名度假游客从斐济外围岛屿上的度假村转移到大陆的酒店<ref name="Tourists Flee">{{cite news | url = http://trove.nla.gov.au/ndp/del/article/122326561 | title = Tourists flee cyclone Sina | newspaper = The Canberra Times | date = 1990-11-28 | accessdate = 2015-04-24 | page = 14 | publisher = National Library of Australia | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130929095155/http://trove.nla.gov.au/ndp/del/article/122326561 | archivedate = 2013-09-29 | deadurl = no | agency = Australian Associated Press }}</ref><ref name="SMH">{{cite news |newspaper=Sydney Morning Herald |title=Hundreds flee path of cyclone; Fiji |author=Sharma, Davendra |author2=Riley, Mark |page=13 |date=1990-11-28 |accessdate=2015-04-24 |archivedate=2015-04-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150424084530/http://newsstore.smh.com.au/apps/viewDocument.ac?page=1&sy=smh&kw=Cyclone%20Sina&pb=all_ffx&dt=selectRange&dr=entire&so=relevance&sf=text&sf=headline&rc=10&rm=200&sp=nrm&clsPage=1&docID=news901128_0128_4382 |url=http://newsstore.smh.com.au/apps/viewDocument.ac?page=1&sy=smh&kw=Cyclone+Sina&pb=all_ffx&dt=selectRange&dr=entire&so=relevance&sf=text&sf=headline&rc=10&rm=200&sp=nrm&clsPage=1&docID=news901128_0128_4382 }}</ref>。[[楠迪国际机场|楠迪国际机场]]和多个地方机场因狂风暴雨被迫关闭<ref name="SMH" />。西纳经过该群岛期间导致部分房屋及其他建筑物受损或被毁，还将树木连根拔起，供电和电话线路因此中断<ref name="Sina TCR" /><ref name="Sina MWL" />。[[瓦努阿岛|瓦努阿岛]]上有一座铁路桥被冲毁，这座桥本是将[[甘蔗|甘蔗]]送往[[拉巴萨|拉巴萨]]制糖厂的必经之路，种植者们别无选择，只能从某村庄借路通过<ref name="Sugar">{{cite news | title = Fiji Methodists sour sugar crop | newspaper = Sunday Herald | date = 1990-12-23 | author = Gaunder, Y}}</ref>。但是，当地[[卫理公会|卫理公会]]教会对这些种植者在周日工作不满，甚至一度以没有遵守星期日法令为由攻击种植者，因此许多工人拒绝在没有得到警察保护的情况下冒然进入村庄<ref name="Sugar" />。汤加受到的影响较小，只有树木、香蕉种植园，以及强度较差的建筑物受到轻度破坏，此外输电和电话线路也受到影响。纽埃和南库克群岛只有部分农作物和建筑物受到轻微损伤。<ref name="Sina TCR" />
